    v0 = 0.20
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.00)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.27 * v0 + 0.92)) / wp.cos(tmp))
    v1 = ((v2 * 0.57) - ((v1 + 0.81 - v2 + 0.03) - 0.84))
